I cannot explain very strange behaviour of the client driver library but I know the cause of my issue:

Oracle DB table SampleTable with column batch_id VARCHAR2(10).

The issue is reproduced when send a query with filter using numeric values. E.g.:
```sql
SELECT * FROM SampleTable WHERE batch_id = 10
